{"commands": [{"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "\n%md-sandbox\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 0; padding-top: 9px;\">\n  <img src=\"https://databricks.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/db-academy-rgb-1200px.png\" alt=\"Databricks Learning\" style=\"width: 1200px\">\n</div>", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "21155e16-8497-4ebf-99bf-5e6c49bb2520", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "be48b0bc-dca2-45d1-bca0-c8796d911e65", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 1, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md-sandbox\n<img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/Apache-Spark-Logo_TM_200px.png\" style=\"float: left: margin: 20px\"/>\n\n# Bronze To Silver - Daily Stock Metrics\n\nWe have to compute and write a table which has the daily high, low and average prices per stock. This one is crucial for our reporting and the visual tool on our application the investors are using regularly.\n\n## In this exercise you:\n* Read from the source, apply business logic and write your result as delta table\n* Learn how to handle transformations and build up metrics\n* Practice sorting on multiple columns\n* Practice aggregating with different aggregations\n* Practice combining aggregation with other builtin functions\n* Practice writing to Delta format\n\n## Prerequisites\n* Web browser: **Chrome**\n* A cluster configured with **8 cores** and **DBR 7.0**", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "87049734-91f8-449b-9674-5251f729e5dc", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "a700b939-4fc3-4072-ae21-afba5d8fb122", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 2, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Classroom-Setup<br>\n\nFor each lesson to execute correctly, please make sure to run the **`Classroom-Setup`** cell at the start of each lesson (see the next cell) and the **`Classroom-Cleanup`** cell at the end of each lesson.", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "8203440e-2206-401e-91b7-042a0e1508f6", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "9e197cc6-ddb0-40f2-b9a1-f1f479a82269", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 3, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%run ./Includes/PCF-14S-ClassroomSetup", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "c2186ef5-b4a0-4d33-b28c-d07fb22dcda3", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "20719cd3-3e3d-4e9c-bcbc-5dcfae0a2d94", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 4, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n## ![Spark Logo Tiny](https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png) Steps to complete<br>\nImplement the function **`challenge()`** to achieve the following:\n- Read the stock orders table from **`silverStockOrdersPath`** into a DataFrame\n- We only need the **`order_timestamp`**, **`ticker`**, **`price`** fields\n- Generate a new column named **`date`** having only the YYYY-MM-DD information by converting the **`order_timestamp`**\n- Aggregate the DataFrame by **`date`** and **`ticker`** to have 3 metrics:\n  * min value of **`price`** named **`low`**, rounded to the second decimal place\n  * max value of **`price`** named **`high`**, rounded to the second decimal place\n  * average value of **`price`** named **`average`**, rounded to the second decimal place\n- Order the result by **`date`** and **`ticker`**\n- Write your result to **`targetDirectory`** as a Delta table using the overwrite mode\n- Return the resulting DataFrame\n\n**`silverStockOrdersPath`** and **`targetDirectory`** have already been defined in your environment.\n\nThe resulting DataFrame schema should look like this:\n\n|name|type|\n|---|---|\n|date|DateType|\n|ticker|StringType|\n|low|DoubleType|\n|high|DoubleType|\n|average|DoubleType|", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "2e6dbd99-5e74-4d8e-b98a-554f3206d0d1", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "04c6de49-97bd-4396-a0ea-fd75a57c7864", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 5, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "// ANSWER\n\ndef solution(spark:org.apache.spark.sql.SparkSession, silverStockOrdersPath:String, targetDirectory:String) : DataFrame = {\n  import org.apache.spark.sql.expressions.Window\n  import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._\n  \n  // Read the stock orders table from `silverStockOrdersPath` into a DataFrame\n  val stockTransactions = (spark.read.format(\"delta\").load(silverStockOrdersPath)\n\n  // We only need the `order_timestamp`, `ticker` and `price` fields\n                            .select(\"order_timestamp\", \"ticker\", \"price\")\n\n  // Generate a new column named `date`** having only the YYYY-MM-DD information by converting the `order_timestamp`\n                            .withColumn(\"date\", col(\"order_timestamp\").cast(\"date\")) \n\n  // Aggregate the DataFrame by `date` and `ticker` to have 3 metrics from price, min, max and average, rounded to the second decimal place\n                            .groupBy(\"date\", \"ticker\")\n                            .agg(round(min(col(\"price\")), 2).alias(\"low\"),\n                                round(max(col(\"price\")), 2).alias(\"high\"),  \n                                round(avg(col(\"price\")), 2).alias(\"average\")\n                           )\n  \n  // Order the result by `date` and `ticker`\n                            .orderBy(\"date\",\"ticker\")\n                       )\n  \n  // Write the resulting DataFrame to `targetDirectory` as a Delta table using the overwrite mode and overwrite schema option.\n  stockTransactions.write.mode(\"overwrite\").format(\"delta\").option(\"overwriteSchema\", \"true\").partitionBy(\"date\").save(targetDirectory) \n  \n  // Return the resulting DataFrame\n  return stockTransactions\n}\nval finalDF = solution(spark, silverStockOrdersPath, targetDirectory)\ndisplay(finalDF)", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "9973210d-b179-4ab1-9522-6e99dbb976b5", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "940828cb-aaa9-4de0-97ae-09a93e915389", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 6, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "%md\n<h2><img src=\"https://files.training.databricks.com/images/105/logo_spark_tiny.png\"> Reality Check</h2>\n\nRun the following cell to make sure you are on track:", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "83b1fc4d-968c-4a5b-9540-47edf76d6421", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid": "be0066de-a8b3-48fe-b7ac-d87b29e9e697", "origId": 0, "parentHierarchy": [], "pivotAggregation": null, "pivotColumns": null, "position": 7, "results": null, "showCommandTitle": false, "startTime": 0, "state": "finished", "streamStates": {}, "submitTime": 0, "subtype": "command", "version": "CommandV1", "width": "auto", "workflows": [], "xColumns": null, "yColumns": null}, {"bindings": {}, "collapsed": false, "command": "// ANSWER - Test the solution\nrealityCheck(solution, spark, silverStockOrdersPath, targetDirectory)", "commandTitle": "", "commandType": "auto", "commandVersion": 0, "commentThread": [], "commentsVisible": false, "customPlotOptions": {}, "datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap": {}, "diffDeletes": [], "diffInserts": [], "displayType": "table", "error": null, "errorSummary": null, "finishTime": 0, "globalVars": {}, "guid": "878fc974-f72f-496a-8402-1d7220465ac5", "height": "auto", "hideCommandCode": false, "hideCommandResult": false, "iPythonMetadata": null, "inputWidgets": {}, "latestUser": "", "latestUserId": null, "nuid"